    <item>
      <title>矿业巨头必和必拓铁矿石产量创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/bhp-iron-ore-shipments-in-line-with-production-guidance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[必和必拓集团有限公司 (BHP Group Ltd.) 的铁矿石产量在截至 6 月底的三个月内增长了 6%，使这家全球矿业巨头的全年产量达到创纪录的 2.6 亿吨，符合预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/bhp-iron-ore-shipments-in-line-with-production-guidance</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 22:34:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
