    <item>
      <title>中国央行利用对冲基金策略遏制债券多头</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/china-s-central-bank-uses-hedge-fund-tactic-to-tame-bond-bulls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行正准备在全球货币政策上进行一次大胆的新尝试——借鉴对冲基金的做法，安排卖空债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/china-s-central-bank-uses-hedge-fund-tactic-to-tame-bond-bulls</guid>
