    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市政债券销售激增，满足了投资者的迫切需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/muni-sales-surge-with-debt-met-by-eager-demand-from-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场越来越预期美联储最早将于 9 月份开始降息，发行人将重点放在降低借贷成本的前景上，市政债券销售额正以数周来最快的速度飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/muni-sales-surge-with-debt-met-by-eager-demand-from-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 18:16:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
